    <h2>Work Experience</h2>
    <div class="content-section__body">
      <article class="experience-entry">
        <header class="experience-entry__header">
          <h3>PHP Developer</h3>
          <p class="experience-entry__meta">
            <span>Russian Express — tour operator</span>
            <a href="https://r-express.ru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">r-express.ru</a>
          </p>
          <p class="experience-entry__period">November 2024 — March 2026</p>
        </header>
        <p>Contributed to the development and maintenance of a B2B travel booking system for agencies and partners. Worked as part of a cross-functional product team including backend developers, an analyst, and a project manager.</p>
        <div class="experience-entry__technologies">
          <p class="experience-entry__label">Technologies:</p>
          <ul class="technology-list">
            <li>PHP 8</li>
            <li>Laravel</li>
            <li>MariaDB</li>
            <li>Redis</li>
            <li>Docker</li>
            <li>Elasticsearch</li>
            <li>GitLab</li>
            <li>Ubuntu</li>
            <li>PhpStorm</li>
