            <li>Contributed to expanding the booking system functionality for new sales markets and B2B partners.</li>
            <li>Improved integrations with ERP/1C and internal services.</li>
            <li>Refactored part of the API interactions from a polling model to a push model to reduce the number of requests to the 1C server.</li>
            <li>Extended the refund and payment transfer mechanism between orders.</li>
            <li>Optimized Elasticsearch usage: improved search logic and contributed to splitting a shared index with 15+ million documents into separate indexes by section.</li>
            <li>Participated in the gradual separation of a monolithic legacy application into internal and external packages.</li>
