    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="content-section__body">
      <p>Contributed to the development and maintenance of web projects for B2B, public sector, non-profit organizations, and corporate clients.</p>
      <ul class="project-list">
        <li>
          <a href="https://renovation.opmoscow.ru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://renovation.opmoscow.ru</a>
          <span>Public program information portal</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://opmoscow.ru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://opmoscow.ru</a>
          <span>Public Chamber of Moscow portal</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://mosvolonter.ru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://mosvolonter.ru</a>
          <span>City volunteer projects platform</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://business-ombudsman.mos.ru" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">https://business-ombudsman.mos.ru</a>
